SubjectAdministrative Fees- Student Loans ** Agreements **
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-417 of March 25, 2010; and (2) approving that the Minister of Employment and Social Development ENTER into AGREEMENTS or ARRANGEMENTS with the governments of the provinces participating under the CANADA STUDENT FINANCIAL ACT, to provide for administrative fees under that Act, substantially in accordance with the schedule.
